Package src2.view

package src2.view
Contains the classes and interfaces responsible for the user interface layer of the Hospital Management System.

This includes views that interact with users, displaying information and handling input for tasks such as viewing appointments, managing inventory, and submitting replenishment requests.

Since:
1.0
